---
title: French Dip Double Burgers with White Cheddar Cheese and Caramelized Onions
description: Hello French Dip! We've given this classic all-American sammie a boost with garlic buns, caramelized onions and melted cheddar cheese. Don't forget the bistro side salad to finish off this mouthwatering meal!

